    <a href="https://marketingland.com/facebook-rolls-out-automated-lead-generation-feature-for-messenger-to-all-advertisers-266386" target="_blank">Learn more</a>

    <h3>New Policies for Elections</h3>
    <p>Ahead of the 2020 elections, Facebook has introduced new policies for political and social issue ads starting mid-Sept. Groups and people placing political advertising will now be subject to a much more detailed verification on the platform to help reduce the spread of online disinformation.</p>

